    dc:description "FIGURES 1–2. Eotetranychus palatiensis sp. nov., 1. Female (dorsum), 2. Lobes on dorsal striation." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2624000/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2624003>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–8. Eotetranychus palatiensis sp. nov., female—3. Distal segment of palpus, 4. Peritremes, 5–6. Genital flaps and pregenital areas, 7. Empodium I, 8. Leg I, left leg, adaxial view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2624003/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2624005>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–15. Eotetranychus palatiensis sp. nov., male—12. Distal segment of palpus, 13. Empodium I, 14. Leg I, left leg, adaxial view, 15. Leg II, left leg, adaxial view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2624005/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2624007>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–22. Eotetranychus palatiensis sp. nov., male—16. Leg III, left leg, adaxial view, 17. Leg IV, right leg, adaxial view, 18. Aedeagus (holotype), 19–22. Aedeagi (paratypes, four variations)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2624007/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

